用。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">视频转代码</span></span></strong></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c1a2675e-f07a-461e-9b87-73020e005900/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.6916666666666667\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"padding: 0px;width: 645px !important;height: 446.125px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100308779\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c1a2675e-f07a-461e-9b87-73020e005900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">基于模型的视频理解能力，它可以从单个 YouTube 视频创建交互式学习应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">就像这样~跟之前模型版本相比，用户界面也更加完善。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d73a6272-06f7-4ab5-c756-0dedbf223400/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.5647058823529412\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1020\" style=\"padding: 0px;width: 645px !important;height: 364.235px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100308786\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d73a6272-06f7-4ab5-c756-0dedbf223400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它在VideoMME 上获得了84.8% 的得分。</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">新功能开发</span></span></strong></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7b335514-f37e-49ce-2ff5-4df2f0ac9e00/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.5509803921568628\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1020\" style=\"padding: 0px;width: 645px !important;height: 355.382px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100308785\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7b335514-f37e-49ce-2ff5-4df2f0ac9e00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">实现新功能意味着需要手动深入设计文件，检查组件以匹配颜色、字体、内边距、外边距和边框等样式属性，然后手动编写所需的 CSS 代码来准确复制这些视觉属性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但现在只需一句提示词，就可以复刻风格，比如添加一个windows 95风格的视频播放器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">除此之外，它还增加了一些新功能，比如听写入门应用，只需说出你的想法，Gemini就能将创意变为现实。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">目前，开发者可以通过Google AI Studio和Vertex AI在 Gemini API 中使用更新的 Gemini 2.5 Pro 开始构建。Gemini App的用户也可以使用它。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.578px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 40px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><em style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-style: italic;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">02</span></em></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 20px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">Gemini取代Gemini</span></strong></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在官方博客中，他们还表示：这个版本原计划在几周后的Google I/O大会上发布，但由于Gemini 2.5太受欢迎，于是决定现在发。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这是基于 Gemini 2.5 Pro编码和多模态推理功能所获得的广泛好评而做出的改进。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">有一说一，Gemini 2.5这一系列确实受到不少关注。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -a