xtstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini取代Gemini</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">是一个信号，表明有些事情已经发生了变化。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">谷歌在各个方面都在稳步发展。头把交椅仍会易主，但巨龙已经苏醒了。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <section style=\"margin:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6d84247-a842-4d3c-5cb6-2601a042e400/public\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.458974358974359\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"780\" style=\"padding: 0px;width: 645px !important;height: 941.038px !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100308784\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f6d84247-a842-4d3c-5cb6-2601a042e400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, -a